700324f-a.title: Bronx: 204th Street (East) - Villa Avenue
700324f-a.text:
(7 East 204th Street, at the N.W. corner ofVilla Ave., showing the
Chiesa Evangelica Italiana; an Italian Presbyterian Church.
May 8, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, ten years later.
May 5, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)

Villa Ave. extending northward.
May 5, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
